The USDGLO Flywheel, a collaboration with Glo Dollar, offers 6,000 USDGLO and 10,000 CELO from June to July 2025 to builders who increase liquidity for Glo Dollar, a stablecoin that donates 100% of its profits to CeloPG. Builders can earn daily rewards by:Launching liquidity pools (LPs) paired with USDGLO.
Integrating USDGLO into lending, staking, or commitment pools.
Launching farms on their dApps with Glo Dollar.

Rewards are paid out daily via Spinach.fi, requiring no lengthy applications or claims, making it a seamless way to earn while building.

